Nestled within the desirable ENCORE AT FISHHAWK RANCH, this 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a den/office is a prime opportunity to embrace 55+ community living  *  The open floor plan creates a welcoming ambiance, leading you to the heart of the home — an impeccably UPGRADED KITCHEN that's a chef's dream  *  Beyond the walls of your new home, Encore presents a treasure trove of ADULT amenities   *   From the lively pickleball courts to the inviting swimming pool (young ones have their own pool!), well-appointed CLUBHOUSE, and a state-of-the-art EXERCISE ROOM, you'll never run out of ways to stay ACTIVE AND SOCIAL  *  The icing on the cake? A dedicated full-time activity director is on-site, curating engaging events and special-interest clubs  *  But the perks don't stop there. This property has an OUTDOOR KITCHEN with decorative STONE ACCENTS, and an EXTENDED LANAI overlooking a SERENE CONSERVATION LOT — ideal for hosting gatherings or savoring the Florida sunshine  *  One of the most attractive features of this property is that GROUNDS MAINTENANCE is provided by the community, meaning you can enjoy your home and its surroundings without the hassle of yard work or landscaping concerns  *  This CAREFREE LIFESTYLE allows you to focus on the things you love and the activities that the Encore at Fishhawk Ranch community offers  *  If you're seeking an UPSCALE 55+ COMMUNITY with a myriad of amenities, a beautifully appointed home, and the ease of maintenance-free living, this property in Encore at Fishhawk Ranch is a true gem.  From the Oasis Club for local activities - a pool (no one under 32 yrs old allowed), clubhouse, fitness center, and pickleball.  Also, a member in The Lake House with beautiful Old Florida setting with game room, fitness center, clubhouse and trails around the lake.  When the young ones come to visit, you have access to Fishhawk West swimming pool with play area, lap pool, and "Central Park' area!  So much to offer!  Seize this chance to make this property your own and relish a delightful, amenity-rich, and maintenance-free way of life in one of Florida's most coveted 55+ communities.
